20fide.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20businessman's%20mindset%20and%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-starship-landing-super-heavy-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20two%20share%20the%20goal%20of%20getting%20humans%20to%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChiao%20hopes%20Isaacman%20can%20speed%20up%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20accepting%20the%20nomination%2C%20Isaacman%20wrote%20that%20NASA%20would%20help%20make%20humanity%20%26quot%3Ba%20true%20spacefaring%20civilization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmericans%20will%20walk%20on%20the%20Moon%20and%20Mars%20and%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20we%20will%20make%20life%20better%20here%20on%20Earth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA%20is%20already%20working%20on%20it.%20The%20Artemis%20program%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebegan%20as%20the%20last%20Trump%20administration's%20iteration%20of%20a%20multi-president%20effort%20to%20send%20humans%20to%20deep%20space%20again.%20Artemis%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaims%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoon-missions-why-astronauts-have-not-returned-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esend%20astronauts%20back%20to%20the%20moon%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%2050%20years%2C%20and%20eventually%20to%20use%20the%20moon%20as%20a%20jumping-off%20point%20to%20send%20people%20to%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Artemis%20is%20years%20behind%20schedule%20and%20billions%20over%20budget%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20technical%20and%20programmatic%20challenges%20with%20the%20giant%20Space%20Launch%20System%20that%20NASA%20is%20building%20for%20moon%20missions.%20Many%20industry%20commentators%20see%20SLS%20as%20a%20waste%20of%20government%20funds%2C%20when%20NASA%20could%20instead%20lean%20on%20commercial%20heavy-lift%20rockets%20like%20Starship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20wid