%20later%20debunked%20confession.%20Here's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20his%20whereabouts%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e04173e-9816-4ebf-aba5-425c39ea0f0d%5C%22%3EJohn%20Mark%20Karr%20used%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BDaxis%26quot%3B%20to%20send%20emails%20to%20a%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20Ramsey%20documentarian%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20and%20Patsy%20Ramsey%2C%20the%20parents%20of%20JonBenet%20Ramsey%2C%20meet%20with%20a%20small%20selected%20group%20of%20the%20local%20Colorado%20media%20after%20four%20months%20of%20silence%20in%20Boulder%2C%20Colorado%20on%20May%201%2C%201997.%20Patsy%20holds%20up%20a%20reward%20sign%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20their%20daughter's%20murderer.%20Their%206-year-old%20daughter%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20Christmas%20night%201996.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67531dfe8fbb2783ed304000%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20and%20Patsy%20Ramsey%20in%20May%201997.%3Cp%3EHelen%20H.%20Richardson%2FThe%20Denver%20Post%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202002%2C%20Michael%20Tracey%2C%20a%20media%20professor%20who%20has%20produced%20several%20documentaries%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfamous-crimes-from-1990s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonBen%C3%A9t%20Ramsey%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20contacted%20via%20email%20by%20a%20man%20using%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BDaxis.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20Tracey%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpassionate%20lover%20of%20little%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20he%20was%20with%20Ramsey%20when%20she%20died%20but%20that%20her%20death%20had%20been%20accidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20communicated%20via%20email%20for%20four%20years.%20Tracey%20eventually%20shared%20his%20communications%20with%20then-Boulder%20DA%20Mary%20Lacy%2C%20after%20Daxis%20appeared%20to%20