ose%20who%20prefer%20clean%20indoor%20backup%20power.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20interested%20in%20preparing%20for%20extreme%20weather%20events%20or%20want%20to%20maintain%20power%20access%20during%20outdoor%20recreation%20activities%2C%20one%20of%20these%20mobile%20units%20will%20get%20the%20job%20done.%20It%20just%20comes%20down%20to%20identifying%20which%20of%20these%20will%20best%20suit%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5908775-57fd-48a3-856e-f49a8ab891a5%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20portable%20generators%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20Nate%20Wade%2C%20merchandise%20manager%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.batteriesplus.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBatteries%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20portable%20generator%20converts%20mechanical%20energy%20into%20electrical%20energy.%E2%80%9D%20By%20using%20an%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20to%20power%20an%20alternator%2C%20these%20machines%20essentially%20allow%20you%20to%20use%20fuel%20(either%20gasoline%2C%20propane%2C%20or%20diesel)%20to%20generate%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20to%20power%20a%20range%20of%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20larger%20fixed%20generators%2C%20portable%20generators%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20easily%20transported%2C%20featuring%20sturdy%20carrying%20handles%20for%20smaller%20models%20and%20wheeled%20bases%20for%20larger%20machines.%20This%20mobility%20makes%20them%20particularly%20useful%20for%20areas%20without%20easy%20access%20to%20power.%20According%20to%20Wade%2C%20outdoor%20events%20(powering%20lighting%20and%20sound%20systems)%2C%20construction%20job%20sites%20where%20temporary%20power%20is%20needed%20for%20tools%20or%20equipment%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20backup%20power%20source%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20outage%20at%20home%2C%20are%20all%20typical%20use%20cases%20for%20a%20portable%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortable%20generators%20can%20vary%20in%20terms%20of%20overall%20power%20output%20(measured%20in%20watt-hours%20(Wh))%2C%20from%20larger%205000-watt%20versions%20that%20can%20power%20larger%20appliances%20like%20refrigerators%20for%208-12%20hours%20to%20smaller%20items%20like%20lights%20and%20fans%20for%2010%2B%20hours%20on%20a%202000-watt%20model.%20With%20standard%20outlets%20identical%20to%20those%20in%20your%20home%2C%20you%20can%20plug%20in%20smaller%20devices%20like%20smartphones%20and%20tablets%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22131fbd76-072c-4777-8c9c-c5c82c4be35c%5C%22%3ETypes%20of%20portable%20generators%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConventional%20generators%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20run%20at%20full%20capacity%20at%20all%20times%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20electrical%20output%20required.%20This%20makes%20them%20louder%20than%20inverter%20generators%20and%20less%20efficient.%20Wade%20added%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20also%20cheaper%2C%20%E2%80%9Cletting%20you%20back%20up%20essential%20functions%20with%20higher%20wattage%20demands%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInverter%20generators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Built%20with%20advanced%20technology%2C%20inverter%20generators%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20adjust%20their%20power%20output%20to%20match%20demand.%20This%20makes%20them%20more%20efficient%2C%20producing%20less%20emissions%20and%20overall%20noise%20than%20conventional%20generators.%20%E2%80%9CInverter%20generators%20are%20also%20more%20compact%20and%20lightweight%20and%20are%20ideal%20for%20powering%20delicate%20electronics%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223c16130-a612-4e7c-b6cf-13194a2b68cd%5C%22%3EPortable%20generator%20pros%20and%20cons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EReliable%20power%20source%20during%20outages%20or%20remote%20use%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERequire%20fuel%20to%20operate%20(an%20added%20expense%20that%20may%20not%20always%20be%20readily%20available)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EConvenient%20to%20transport%20and%20setup%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ENoisy%20operation%20and%20fumes%20mean%20it%20cannot%20be%20used%20indoors%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EAvailable%20in%20a%20range%20of%20capacity%20options%20for%20different%20needs.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERequires%20regular%20maintenance%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-portable-generator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20portable%20generators%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2d5f2ab-2917-4715-8e5a-fe454eccae8b%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20power%20stations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20power%20station%20(also%20called%20a%20portable%20power%20generator)%20is%20a%20rechargeable%20battery%20system%20that%20can%20power%20electronic%20devices%20and%20appliances.%20According%20to%20Wade%2C%20these%20devices%20store%20electricity%20in%20built-in%20rechargeable%20batteries%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20be%20charged%20via%20wall%20outlets%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20or%20even%20car%20chargers%E2%80%9D.%20They%20typically%20feature%20multiple%20output%20options%20like%20AC%20outlets%2C%20USB%20ports%2C%20and%20DC%20outputs%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20charging%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWade%20explained%20that%20some%20power%20stations%20use%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20while%20others%20use%20newer%20battery%20chemistries%20like%20lithium%20iron%20phosphate%20(LiFePO4).%20These%20newer%20batteries%20provide%20increased%20thermal%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20naturally%20increasing%20their%20overall%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20longer%20lifespan%20than%20standard%20lithium-ion%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20quiet%20operation%20and%20portability%20make%20power%20stations%20ideal%20for%20off-grid%20activities%20like%20camping%20or%20road%20trips%20that%20benefit%20from%20reduced%20noise%20levels.%20Since%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20generate%20any%20fumes%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20also%20ideal%20for%20indoor%20use%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20convenient%20for%20powering%20phones%2C%20laptops%2C%20and%20other%20electronics%20in%20an%20emergency.%20While%20there%20aren%E2%80%99t%20specific%20types%20of%20power%20stations%20(like%20portable%20generators)%2C%20they%20do%20come%20in%20a%20range%20of%20capacities%2C%20which%20can%20help%20customers%20determine%20which%20is%20best%20for%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229582c875-1aca-458f-9105-4604b2a0f190%5C%22%3ETypes%20of%20Power%20Stations%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmall%20(under%20300Wh)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20compact%20models%20are%20best%20for%20charging%20smaller%20items%20like%20laptops%2C%20smartphones%2C%20smartwatches%2C%20and%20tablets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedium%20(300%20-%201000Wh)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20smaller%20items%2C%20these%20can%20power%20small%20appliances%20like%20small%20fans%2C%20CPAP%20machines%2C%20LED%20lights%2C%20and%20coffee%20makers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELarge%20(over%201000Wh)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epower%20stations%20can%20handle%20high-draw%20appliances%20like%20refrigerators%2C%20electric%20grills%2C%20window%20unit%20AC%20units%2C%20or%20multiple%20smaller%20items%20at%20once.%20(Although%20actual%20runtime%20depends%20on%20the%20amount%20and%20wattage%20requirements%20of%20the%20item's%20drawing%20power).%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7763551-8bc1-4612-90ed-afd40a5ccd95%5C%22%3EPower%20station%20pros%20and%20cons%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EQuiet%20operation%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20combustion%20engine%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ELess%20capacity%20compared%20to%20portable%20generators%20translates%20to%20shorter%20runtime%20for%20larger%20appliances%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ECan%20be%20recharged%20through%20a%20variety%20of%20methods%2C%20such%20as%20AC%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20or%20car%20charging%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ESlow%20to%20recharge%20(especially%20if%20using%20solar%20panels)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ECan%20be%20used%20indoors%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20harmful%20fumes%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ELarger%20capacity%20models%20can%20be%20very%20expensive%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22889a0f48-56bb-4beb-b8f7-5dae7c0b645e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortable%20generator%20vs.%20power%20stations%3A%20The%20differences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20difference%20between%20portable%20generators%20and%20power%20stations%20is%20their%20power%20source.%20Generators%20run%20on%20fuel%2C%20such%20as%20gas%20or%20propane%2C%20while%20power%20stations%20run%20on%20stored%20battery%20power.%20This%20means%20that%20generators%20are%20more%20suited%20to%20power%20outages%20since%20their%20power%20source%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20access%20to%20a%20working%20power%20grid.%20When%20power%20stations%20are%20depleted%20in%20an%20outage%2C%20they%20must%20either%20source%20energy%20from%20another%20power%20station%20or%20use%20a%20solar%20panel%20system%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20which%20are%20much%20less%20convenient%20to%20source%20than%20gas%20or%20propane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortable%20generators%20also%20generally%20cost%20much%20less%20than%20power%20stations.%20Prices%20of%20both%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20capacity%20and%20functionality%2C%20but%20in%20general%2C%20power%20stations%20cost%20roughly%20two%20to%20three%20times%20more%20than%20generators%20of%20similar%20wattage.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20generators%20require%20additional%20fuel%20costs%20to%20keep%20them%20running%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20much%20higher%20than%20power%20stations%20(based%20on%20the%20average%20electricity%20rate%20of%20%24.12%2FkWh).%20Solar%20charging%20has%20no%20direct%20cost%20but%20requires%20a%20solar%20panel%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%20capacity%20is%20another%20big%20difference%2C%20with%20portable%20generators%20typically%20offering%20more%20watt%20hours%20than%20power%20stations.%20Wade%20explains%20that%20this%20means%20%E2%80%9Cgenerators%20offer%20higher%20power%20output%20for%20longer%20periods%2C%20while%20power%20stations%20are%20more%20suited%20to%20small%20devices%20and%20shorter%20usage%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoise%20and%20emissions%20are%20the%20clearest%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20options.%20The%20combustion%20engine%20of%20a%20portable%20generator%20produces%20high%20noise%20levels%20and%20potentially%20deadly%20carbon%20monoxide%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dsoelectric.com%2Fportable-generator-produces-much-co-parking-lot-cars%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFiring%2520up%2520one%2520fuel%252Dpowered%2Cthe%2520Consumer%2520Product%2520Safety%2520Commission.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuch%20more%20than%20an%20automobile%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Because%20of%20these%20factors%20(particularly%20the%20high%20risk%20of%20carbon%20monoxide%20poisoning)%2C%20generators%20cannot%20be%20used%20indoors.%20Power%20stations%20run%20with%20almost%20zero%20noise%20and%20no%20emissions%20and%20can%20be%20used%20indoors%20without%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerators%20are%20also%20generally%20much%20larger%2C%20heavier%2C%20and%20more%20challenging%20to%20transport%20than%20power%20stations.%20This%20superior%20portability%20makes%20power%20stations%20much%20more%20convenient%20to%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use%20and%20to%20carry%20to%20and%20from%20a%20vehicle%20or%20different%20area%20of%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortable%20Generator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20Station%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERange%20from%20%24400%20to%20%242000%2C%20with%20many%20high-performance%20options%20below%20%241000.%20Requires%20additional%20fuel%20expense.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERoughly%202%20to%203x%20more%20expensive%20than%20generators%20of%20similar%20wattage%20output.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERequires%20fuel%20mixing%2Fhandling%20as%20well%20as%20fuel%20storage%2C%20must%20be%20used%20outdoors%2C%20some%20require%20a%20pull-start%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EPlug-and-play%20charging%2C%20always%20push%20button%20start%2C%20safe%20to%20use%20indoors%2C%20practically%20zero%20maintenance.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20Generation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EGas%20and%20propane%20allow%20for%20continuous%20operation%20during%20power%20outages%2C%20and%20are%20relatively%20easy%20to%20locate%20and%20purchase.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERequires%20an%20additional%20electrical%20power%20source%20to%20recharge.%20In%20a%20power%20outage%2C%20must%20rely%20on%20car%20charging%20or%20a%20slow-working%20solar%20panel%20system.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ECombustible%20gas%20and%20propane%20can%20be%20dangerous%20if%20improperly%20handled%2C%20and%20emissions%20pose%20a%20carbon%20monoxide%20poisoning%20risk%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EZero%20emissions%20mean%20no%20risk%20of%20CO%20poisoning%2C%20but%20if%20punctured%20or%20damaged%2C%20the%20internal%20batteries%20can%20ignite%20or%20explode.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EHeavy%20weight%20and%20bulky%20shape%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20lift%20and%20carry.%20Large%20size%20is%20less%20convenient%20to%20store.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ESmaller%20and%20lighter%20than%20most%20portable%20generators%20(depending%20on%20the%20capacity).%20More%20compact%20size%20is%20easier%20to%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%20%26amp%3B%20Emissions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EThe%20combustion%20engine%20is%20very%20noisy%20and%20generates%20excessive%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20monoxide.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ENear-silent%20operation%20and%20with%20no%20engine%2C%20generates%20zero%20emissions.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ERequire%20regular%20oil%20changes%20every%2050-100%20hours%2C%20as%20well%20as%20occasional%20air%20filter%2C%20fuel%20filter%2C%20and%20spark%20plug%20replacement.%20Carburetor%20cleaning%20necessary%20if%20fuel%20sits%20for%20too%20long.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EOnly%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20clean%20and%20dry.%20Battery%20may%20need%20to%20be%20replaced%20after%203-5%20years.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282ff4bd0-b316-43fc-be52-ab87d9762986%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nutshell%2C%20while%20generators%20are%20more%20powerful%20and%20run%20longer%2C%20power%20stations%20are%20significantly%20easier%20to%20use%20and%20maintain.%20For%20those%20whose%20top%20priority%20is%20emergency%20use%20in%20a%20power%20outage%20and%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20hindered%20by%20limited%20runtime%20or%20slow%20solar%20charging%2C%20a%20portable%20generator%20is%20the%20best%20choice.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you%E2%80%99re%20comfortable%20handling%20the%20maintenance%20requirements%20and%20aware%20of%20the%20carbon%20monoxide%20risk%20(these%20emissions%20can%20affect%20those%20inside%20your%20home%2C%20even%20when%20used%20within%2020%20feet%20of%20a%20window).%20If%20convenient%20transport%20and%20short-term%2C%20portable%20power%20is%20your%20goal%2C%20go%20with%20a%20power%20station.%20Just%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20limited%20capacity%20is%20still%20sufficient%20to%20power%20your%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fportable-generator-vs-power-station%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%