%2Fconnor-franta-coming-out-video-2014-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConnor%20Franta%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20suing%20his%20business%20partners%2C%20alleging%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20they%20embezzled%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20from%20the%20company%20they%20cofounded%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20suit%2C%20filed%20in%20California%20Superior%20Court%20this%20week%2C%20Franta%20%E2%80%94%20a%2032-year-old%20YouTuber%20with%204.8%20million%20subscribers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20suing%20his%20cofounders%20in%20Heard%20Well%2C%20a%20music%20label%20that%20works%20with%20influencers.%20He%20also%20names%20the%20company's%20business%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20the%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20cofounders%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20defendant%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20alleged%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20partners%20and%20manager%20all%20denied%20the%20allegations%20in%20statements%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20alleges%20Heard%20Well%20cofounder%20Jeremy%20Wineberg%20used%20an%20American%20Express%20Black%20Card%20obtained%20in%20the%20company's%20name%20for%20personal%20expenses%2C%20including%20international%20travel%2C%20concert%20tickets%2C%20tattoos%2C%20groceries%2C%20and%20plastic%20surgery.%20The%20suit%20says%20Wineberg%20%26quot%3Bsystematically%20looted%20the%20company%20of%20essentially%20every%20penny%2C%26quot%3B%20using%20Heard%20Well%20funds%20to%20pay%20the%20Amex%20balances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20cofounder%2C%20Franta's%20former%20CAA%20agent%20Andrew%20Graham%2C%20also%20%26quot%3Bconverted%20thousands%20of%20Heard%20Well%20dollars%26quot%3B%20for%20personal%20use%2C%20the%20suit%20alleges.%20The%20suit%20says%20Graham%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bthe%20principal%20bad%20actor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECAA%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-influencer-agents-managers-database-youtube-instagram-tiktok%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20Hollywood%20talent%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20digital%20arm%20that%20represents%20influencers%20on%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20TikTok.%20The%20agency%20works%20with%20creators%20to%20monetize%20their%20followings%20through%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20consumer%20products%2C%20and%20other%20business%20ventures.%20CAA%20is%20not%20named%20as%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWineberg%2C%20and%20to%20a%20lesser%20extent%20Graham%2C%20used%20the%20company's%20earnings%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20de%20facto%20personal%20piggy%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Franta%2C%20in%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20said%20Lindsay%20Wineberg%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%20%E2%80%94%20Heard%20Well's%20business%20manager%20and%20accountant%2C%20led%20by%20Jeremy%20Wineberg's%20father%20%E2%80%94%20acted%20negligently%20by%20turning%20the%20other%20cheek%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20in%20doing%20so%20negligently%20facilitated%20the%20draining%20of%20over%20%241%20million%20of%20company%20monies%20into%20the%20personal%20pockets%20of%20Wineberg%20(and%20Graham).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Sullivan%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Jeremy%20Wineberg%20and%20Lindsay%20Wineberg%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%2C%20said%20the%20allegations%20aren't%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20Connor%20Franta%20is%20without%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%20Sullivan%20said%20his%20clients%20never%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20in%20any%20misconduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20pursue%20all%20of%20our%20rights%20and%20expect%20to%20be%20vindicated%20in%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Shenk%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Graham%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20his%20client%20%26quot%3Bdenies%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20complaint%20and%20looks%20forward%20to%20defending%20this%20case%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20no%20longer%20represents%20Franta%2C%20nor%20does%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranta%20has%20been%20on%20YouTube%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20and%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%20the%20memoir%20%26quot%3BA%20Work%20in%20Progress.%26quot%3B%20He%20cofounded%20Heard%20Well%20in%202015%2C%20with%20each%20of%20the%20cofounders%20contributing%20%242%2C000%20to%20capitalize%20the%20startup%2C%20according%20to%20an%20operating%20agreement%20that%20was%20filed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeard%20Well%20published%20dozens%20of%20albums%2C%20but%20Franta%20%26quot%3Bhardly%20saw%20a%20dime%20of%20profit%20directed%20his%20way%20throughout%20the%20company's%20nearly%2010-year%20lifespan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20spring%2C%20the%20suit%20says%2C%20Franta%20learned%20Heard%20Well%20had%20fallen%20behind%20on%20royalty%20payments%20after%20a%20YouTube%20video%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20scamming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeard%20Well's%20Instagram%20account%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDDNvkLqSMKS%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactive%20as%20of%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20Franta%20said%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20he's%20been%20blocked%20from%20the%20company's%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActing%20with%20integrity%20and%20respect%20in%20all%20my%20professional%20endeavors%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20fellow%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20has%20always%20been%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Franta%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20the%20matter%20had%20only%20recently%20come%20to%20his%20attention%2C%20he'd%20taken%20action%20this%20week%20%26quot%3Bto%20protect%20the%20company%20and%20to%20facilitate%20its%20pursuit%20of%20all%20necessary%20and%20appropriate%20legal%20remedies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20