.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fboston-city-councilor-tania-fernandes-anderson-arrested-on-federal-fraud-charges%2Famp_articleshow%2F116056300.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B'Ninda%20Ras%20Increasing%26quot%3B%3A%20Poll%20Body%20Chief%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20Amid%20Complaints%20Over%20EVMs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20praise%20or%20see%20the%20positives%20is%20on%20a%20decline%2C%20noted%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20criticism%20(%3Cem%3Eninda%20ras%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%20The%20comment%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20questions%20over%20the%20voting%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20NDTV%20'Indian%20of%20the%20Year%20Awards%202024'%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20even%20though%20conducting%20the%20elections%20can%20be%20logistically%20challenging%2C%20the%20voters%20of%20the%20country%20are%20capable%20of%20resolving%20all%20issues%20in%20a%20peaceful%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20surprises%20me%2C%20positively%2C%20is%20the%20resilience%20of%20the%20Indian%20voter...%20this%20country%20can%20resolve%20all%20its%20issues%20peacefully%20through%20the%20ballot%2C%20not%20the%20bullet...%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20satisfaction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20several%20polling%20personnel%20were%20honoured%20with%20the%20NDTV%20'Indian%20of%20the%20Year%20Awards%202024'%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bpresiding%20officers%20who%20keep%20the%20democracy%20alive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%2010%2C50%2C000%20booths%20in%20the%20country.%20Each%20booth%20comprises%20around%20four%20to%20five%20presiding%20officers.%20This%20makes%20it%20around%2050%2C00%2C000%20fellows.%20And%20who%20are%20these%20people%3F%20You've%20seen%20them%20-%20they%20are%20teachers%2C%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20agricultural%20department...%20people%20are%20pooled%20from%20various%20departments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20entire%20country's%20workforce%20is%20at%20the%20service%20of%20the%20poll%20commission%20during%20the%20elections.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20team%20of%20500-600%20people%20in%20the%20commission.%20During%20the%20elections%2C%20we%20become%2015%20million...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20official%20of%20the%20polling%20body%20explained%20how%20the%20presiding%20officers%20are%20%26quot%3Brandomly%26quot%3B%20deputed%20to%20various%20polling%20booths%20across%20the%20country%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20political%20party%20leaders%20and%20their%20agents%2C%20to%20avoid%20allegations%20of%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world's%20highest%20polling%20station%20is%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%20opposite%20south%2C%20there%20is%20another%20huge%20part%20of%20India...%20in%20the%20west%2C%20you%20have%20the%20desert%2C%20and%20in%20the%20east%2C%20you%20have%20the%20wettest%20place%20in%20the%20world%2C%20where%20we%20have%20the%20polling%20station.%20The%20machine%20(EVMs)%20works%20in%20the%20desert%2C%20under%20zero%20degree%20temperatures%2C%20under%20moisture-laden%20conditions...%20So%20long%20as%20they%20(polling%20personnel)%20are%20there%2C%20Indian%20democracy%20is%20absolutely%20in%20safe%20hands%20and%20perfect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20often%20accused%20the%20poll%20body%20of%20bias%20and%20raised%20doubts%20over%20the%20functioning%20of%20voting%20machines.%20After%20losing%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Congress%20alleged%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20and%20manipulation%20of%20the%20voting%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20recently%2C%20disapproved%20of%20repeated%20doubts%20raised%20over%20the%20voting%20machines%2C%20berating%20the%20tendency%20of%20political%20parties%20to%20raise%20doubts%20over%20their%20functioning%20whenever%20they%20lose%20elections%20while%20conveniently%20accepting%20the%20system%20when%20they%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20lamented%20that%20despite%20efforts%2C%20voters%20in%20cities%20continue%20to%20avoid%20turning%20up%20at%20polling%20stations%20on%20election%20days.%20While%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Naxal-affected%20areas%20have%20witnessed%20high%20turnout%2C%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20in%20cities%20do%20not%20vote%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20several%20initiatives%20by%20the%20polling%20commission%2C%20voters%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Gurugram%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20in%20large%20numbers%20at%20the%20booths%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColaba%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20registered%20the%20lowest%20turnout%20in%20the%20recently-held%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20urban%20apathy%20and%20youth%20apathy%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20in%20times%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733511840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Flripr6tg_cec-rajiv-kumar_625x300_07_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fninda-ras-increasing-election-commission-chief-rajiv-kumar-amid-complaints-over-evms-7190017%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ability%20to%20praise%20or%20see%20the%20positives%20is%20on%20a%20decline%2C%20noted%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20criticism%20(ninda%20ras)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fninda-ras-increasing-election-commission-chief-rajiv-kumar-amid-complaints-over-evms-7190017%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22