r%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fashamed-to-be-an-american-teacher-claims-she-was-fired-for-posting-anti-trump-content-on-social-media%2Farticleshow%2F116050424.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fashamed-to-be-an-american-teacher-claims-she-was-fired-for-posting-anti-trump-content-on-social-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F116050424.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fashamed-to-be-an-american-teacher-claims-she-was-fired-for-posting-anti-trump-content-on-social-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F116050424.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%201st%2C%20BJP%20Says%20US%20State%20Department%20Behind%20%26quot%3BDeep%20State%26quot%3B%20Targeting%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20or%20BJP%2C%20which%20leads%20the%20coalition%20of%20parties%20currently%20in%20Government%20in%20India%2C%20has%20directly%20accused%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bdestabilise%20India%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20state%26quot%3B%20is%20working%20to%20%26quot%3Btarget%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20always%20been%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20behind%20this%20agenda%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20CLAIMS%20THERE'S%20A%20NEXUS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambit%20Patra%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20claimed%20that%20elements%20in%20the%20US%20deep%20state%20have%20colluded%20with%20a%20group%20of%20journalists%20and%20with%20India's%20opposition%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20put%20a%20spoke%20in%20the%20wheel%20of%20India's%20growth%20story%20with%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20and%20malicious%20reports%20without%20a%20%26quot%3Bshred%20of%20evidence%26quot%3B.%20He%20suggested%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20all%20this%20is%20in%20conjunction%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BUS%20State%20Department%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20slammed%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20using%20reports%20by%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20or%20OCCRP%20that%20%26quot%3Bsingularly%20focused%26quot%3B%20on%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20its%20alleged%20closeness%20to%20the%20government%20to%20undermine%20PM%20Modi%20-%20all%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20charges%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20without%20a%20%26quot%3Bshred%20of%20evidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20spokesperson%20then%20cited%20a%20French%20media%20report%20that%20showed%20that%20OCCRP%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20and%20%26quot%3Bother%20deep%20state%20figures%26quot%3B%20like%20George%20Soros.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Deep%20State%20had%20a%20clear%20objective%20to%20destabilise%20India%20by%20targeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20always%20been%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20behind%20this%20agenda...OCCRP%20has%20served%20as%20a%20media%20tool%20for%20carrying%20out%20a%20deep%20state%20agenda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20French%20investigative%20media%20group%20has%20revealed%20that%2050%25%20of%20OCCRP's%20funding%20comes%20directly%20from%20the%20US%20State%20Department%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20spokesperson%20then%20accused%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%20of%20the%20highest%20order%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20agencies%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20and%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20triangle%20trying%20to%20destabilise%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambit%20Patra's%20charge%20was%20then%20repeated%20by%20his%20party%20colleague%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20in%20Parliament.%20Mr%20Dubey%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20with%20foreign%20forces%26quot%3B%20to%20derail%20the%20government%20because%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%20called%20for%20opposition%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20be%20thoroughly%20investigated%20for%20meeting%20with%20controversial%20business%20tycoon%20George%20Soros%2C%20who%20he%20claimed%20%26quot%3Broutinely%20conspires%20to%20derail%20economies%20of%20other%20countries%26quot%3B%20and%20American%20lawmakers%20like%20Ilhan%20Omar%2C%20who%20have%20strongly%20opposed%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20administration.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20must%20answer...%20what%20transpired%20in%20meetings%20with%20those%20who%20have%20a%20history%20of%20peddling%20anti-India%20agenda%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20foreign%20tours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECONGRESS%20RESPONDS%2C%20DEMANDS%20APOLOGY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resulted%20in%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20called%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20unfortunate%20incident%26quot%3B.%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20slammed%20Mr%20Dubey%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%20statement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%201%2C%20you%20cannot%20attack%20people%20in%20a%20defamatory%20manner.%20No%202%2C%20you%20cannot%20take%20anyone's%20name%20without%20giving%20them%20notice%20in%20writing%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20No%203%2C%20you%20cannot%20assault%20parliamentary%20privilege.%20He%20violated%20all%20those%20three%20rules%20and%20he%20was%20allowed%20to%20go%20on%20speaking%20and%20ranting%20for%20quite%20some%20time...%20so%20we%20objected%20to%20that.%20The%20House%20was%20initially%20adjourned.%20We%20went%20to%20see%20the%20Speaker%20and%20we%20said%20thi