20health%20and%20seek%20to%20answer%20them%20-%20which%20was%20evident%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20-%20Dr%20Gagandeep%20Kang%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20top%20virologists%2C%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kang%2C%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20'Health%20Leader%20Of%20The%20Year'%20award%20at%20the%20NDTV%20Indian%20Of%20The%20Year%20awards%20on%20Friday%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20long%20Covid%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20yoga%20in%20tackling%20the%20rise%20of%20lifestyle%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20receiving%20the%20award%2C%20Dr%20Kang%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20borrow%20our%20solutions%20from%20the%20West%20and%20what%20we%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20do%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20is%20for%20us%20to%20frame%20our%20own%20questions%20about%20health%20in%20India%20and%20seek%20to%20answer%20them.%20I%20am%20really%20excited%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20finally%20doing%20that%3B%20we%20saw%20it%20during%20Covid%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20that%20this%20is%20a%20revolution%20that%20will%20continue%20because%20we%20do%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20ourselves%20to%20be%20able%20to%20solve%20our%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kang%20said%20there%20are%20two%20areas%20that%20she%20would%20like%20to%20see%20India%20focus%20on%2C%20including%20solving%20tuberculosis%20(TB)%20in%20the%20country.%20She%20said%20TB%20is%20the%20biggest%20infectious%20disease%20killer%20in%20the%20world%20and%20Covid%20had%20beaten%20it%20for%20a%20year%2C%20but%20it%20is%20now%20back.%20The%20second%20area%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20nutrition%20-%20both%20under-%20and%20over-nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virologist%20also%20spoke%20about%20integrating%20traditional%20Indian%20systems%20of%20medicine%20and%20knowledge%2C%20which%20have%20not%20been%20fully%20integrated%20into%20healthcare%2C%20prompting%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20she%20sees%20the%20dissonance%20between%20traditional%20and%20modern%20medicine%20reducing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20with%20the%20increase%20of%20westernised%20lifestyles%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20more%20lifestyle%20diseases%20and%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20traditional%20systems%20of%20medicine%2C%20they%20are%20holistic%20in%20the%20advice%20that%20they%20offer%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20diet%2C%20exercise%20and%20what%20people%20need%20to%20be%20doing.%20Yoga%20is%20union%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kang%20said%20she%20chose%20research%20as%20her%20field%20because%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20exciting%20than%20the%20opportunity%20to%20ask%20your%20own%20questions%20and%20then%20figure%20out%20the%20answers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lot%20Of%20Work%20To%20Do'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Covid%2C%20its%20mutations%20and%20long%20Covid%2C%20which%20is%20still%20affecting%20many%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20are%20learning%20more%20about%20long%20Covid%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20viral%20infections.%20We%20clubbed%20it%20all%20as%20one%20syndrome%20and%20what%20we%20are%20learning%20today%20is%20that%20it%20actually%20has%20multiple%20manifestations%20that%20can%20last%20long%20term.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20for%20us%20to%20do%20to%20understand%20the%20consequences%20of%20both%20single%20and%20multiple%20infections%2C%20which%20is%20the%20situation%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20she%20had%20a%20message%20for%20young%20girls%20who%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20science%2C%20the%20virologist%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEconomic%20independence%20really%20matters%20and%20if%20you%20can%20achieve%20that%20doing%20something%20that%20you%20enjoy%2C%20you%20are%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20for%20yourself%20and%20your%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733496000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h