0Bangladesh%20in%20the%20final%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20clinching%20their%20ninth%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733493300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fvbfcfn28_vaibhav-suryavanshi-x-sonyliv_625x300_06_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F6-6-4-6-13-year-old-india-star-vaibhav-suryavanshi-goes-berserk-in-31-run-over-vs-sri-lanka-in-under-19-asia-cup-semi-final-watch-7187955%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirteen-year-old%20cricketing%20prodigy%20Vaibhav%20Suryavanshi%20continues%20to%20make%20headlines%20in%20the%20U19%20Asia%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F6-6-4-6-13-year-old-india-star-vaibhav-suryavanshi-goes-berserk-in-31-run-over-vs-sri-lanka-in-under-19-asia-cup-semi-final-watch-7187955%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20It%20Means%20For%20Bangladesh%20To%20Drop%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20From%20Currency%20Notes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangabandhu%20(friend%20of%20Bangladesh)%20-%20the%20name%20by%20which%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20had%20been%20known%2C%20seems%20quite%20ironic%20to%20what's%20happening%20there%2C%20since%20the%20country%20identifies%20him%20as%20a%20nemesis%20now.%20Bangladesh%20is%20set%20to%20erase%20the%20image%20of%20Rahman%2C%20the%20iconic%20founding%20father%20of%20the%20country%2C%20from%20its%20currency%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20aim%20to%20release%20the%20new%20notes%20within%20the%20next%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Husneara%20Shikha%2C%20Executive%20Editor%20of%20Bangladesh%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20big%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20Bangladesh%20government%20because%20Rahman%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20currency%20since%20the%20country's%20inception%20on%20March%204th%2C%201972.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Hasina%20fled%20Bangladesh%20after%20the%20student-led%20protests%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20a%20Nobel%20laureate%2C%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20Chief%20Adviser%20of%20an%20interim%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20ousting%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Bangladesh%20is%20set%20to%20remove%20her%20father%2C%20from%20the%20face%20of%20Bangladesh%20currency%20and%20print%20new%20notes%20Taka%2020%2C%20100%2C%20500%2C%20and%201%2C000%20-%20as%20Bangladesh%20Bank%20has%20confirmed.%20This%20takes%20place%20just%20weeks%20after%20Rahman's%20portrait%20was%20taken%20down%20from%20Yunus'%20office%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bconcession%26quot%3B%20given%20to%20the%20student%20protesters%20from%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahfuz%20Alam%2C%20an%20adviser%20to%20the%20government%2C%20said%20%26quot%3BPhoto%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman-%20Post%20'71%20Fascist%2C%20is%20removed%20from%20Darbar%20Hall.%20It%20is%20a%20shame%20for%20us%20that%20we%20couldn't%20remove%20his%20picture%20from%20Bangabhaban%20after%20the%205th%20August.%20Apologies.%20But%2C%20he%20won't%20be%20seen%20anywhere%20till%20people's%20July%20spirit%20lives%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20has%20further%20added%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bgraffiti%26quot%3B%20drawn%20during%20the%20July%20protests%2C%20with%20some%20religious%20structures%20and%20Bengali%20traditions%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20designing%20of%20the%20new%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20can%20be%20perceived%20as%20the%20country%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20shift%20from%20its%20identity%20and%20the%20legacy%20of%20Bangabandhu.%20It%20is%20also%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20a%20national%20holiday%20on%20August%2015th%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%20since%20that%20day%20marked%20the%20assassination%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20several%20institutions%20have%20been%20renamed%2C%20removing%20Hasina%20and%20Rahman%20from%20their%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3