out%20becoming%20cramped.%20Ensure%20the%20pot%20has%20a%20drainage%20hole%20to%20prevent%20waterlogging%2C%20a%20common%20cause%20of%20root%20rot%20in%20strawberry%20plants.%20A%20well-draining%20pot%20ensures%20the%20roots%20receive%20the%20necessary%20oxygen%20for%20healthy%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Creating%20the%20ideal%20potting%20mix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20the%20perfect%20potting%20mix%20is%20key%20to%20providing%20your%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrawberry%20plants%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20nutrients%20they%20need%20to%20flourish.%20Use%20cow%20dung%2C%20cocopeat%2C%20and%20neem%20cake%20in%20your%20potting%20mix%20to%20provide%20essential%20nutrients%2C%20aeration%2C%20and%20natural%20fungicide%20to%20protect%20the%20plants%20from%20fungal%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20cocopeat%20is%20unavailable%2C%20a%20substitute%20mix%20can%20be%20prepared%20by%20combining%20fine-grained%20soil%20with%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20sand.%20This%20combination%20ensures%20good%20drainage%20and%20aeration%2C%20mimicking%20the%20benefits%20of%20cocopeat.%20The%20crucial%20aspect%20is%20to%20maintain%20a%20well-draining%20and%20airy%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20juicy%20fruits%20are%20loaded%20with%20vitamins%2C%20fibre%2C%20antioxidants%2C%20and%20minerals.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia