nk.%20The%20reason%2C%20they%20say%2C%20lies%20in%20balancing%20proportions%2C%20knowing%20how%20much%20is%20too%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20deep%20dive%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20four%20projects%20which%20endorse%20materials%20that%20claim%20to%20be%20more%20sustainable%20than%20cement%2C%20whilst%20also%20exploring%20their%20viability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Autoclaved%20aerated%20concrete%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20material%20fulfils%20the%20demand%20for%20longevity%2C%20insulation%20(contributed%20by%20the%20bubbles%20and%20voids%20in%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20structure)%20and%20structural%20integrity.%20Autoclaved%20aerated%20concrete%20(AAC)%20is%20one%20of%20architect%20Vivek%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20favourites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20previously%20worked%20with%20the%20material%20for%20one%20of%20New%20Delhi-based%20REPL%E2%80%99s%20(Rudrabhishek%20Enterprises%20Limited)%20projects%2C%20Vivek%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20its%20light-weightness%20and%20thermal%20insulation%20properties.%20%E2%80%9CIts%20high%20fire%20resistance%20and%20sound%20insulation%20also%20enhance%20building%20safety%20and%20comfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Studies%20agree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F1