a%20major%20contributor%20and%20needs%20to%20stop%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20struggles%20with%20pollution%2C%20looking%20at%20cities%20that%20have%20successfully%20tackled%20the%20issue%20could%20provide%20solutions.%20Barcelona%2C%20which%20has%20greatly%20improved%20its%20air%20quality%2C%20offers%20valuable%20lessons%20for%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPedestrian-friendly%20%E2%80%98Superblocks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20cities%20throughout%20the%20late%2020th%20century%2C%20Barcelona%20has%20managed%20to%20reduce%20its%20air%20pollution%20with%20the%20help%20of%20progressive%20urban%20planning%2C%20transportation%20reforms%2C%20and%20green%20initiatives.%20In%202019%2C%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20mean%20annual%20PM%20particulate%20matter%20concentration%20was%2017%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%2C%20exceeding%20the%2010%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%20limit.%20Today%2C%20their%20real-time%20PM2.5%20level%20is%206%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20city%20have%20lowered%20the%20levels%20of%20particulate%20matter%20and%20made%20it%20more%20livable%20and%20sustainable.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20strategies%20in%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20air%20pollution%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98superblock%E2%80%99%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20urban%20planning%20approach%20divides%20city%20streets%20into%20octagonal%20blocks.%20Inside%20these%20blocks%2C%20only%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381023%2Fbhubaneswar-odisha-best-public-transport-india-crut-sustainable-urban-mobility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20transport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20allowed%2C%20while%20cars%20can%20only%20use%20the%20outer%20streets.%20This%20reduces%20traffic%2C%20lowers%20vehicle%20emissions%2C%20and%20improves%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Barcelona%20showcasing%20its%20superblocks%2C%20with%20green%20spaces%20and%20pedestrian-friendly%20streets%20within%20the%20octagonal%20city%20blocks.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-300x146.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-500x244.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-768x374.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-150x73.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384042%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESuperblocks%20are%20octagonal%20city%20blocks%20for%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20public%20transport%2C%20with%20cars%20restricted%20to%20outer%20streets%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Representational%20image)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20main%20causes%20of%20air%20pollution%20that%20contribute%20almost%2050%25%20are%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20industrial%20activities%2C%20construction%2C%20garbage%20burning%2C%20and%20emissions%20from%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Barcelona%2C%20each%20superblock%20covers%20an%20area%20of%20400%C3%97400%20metres%2C%20which%20is%20larger%20than%20a%20city%20block%20but%20smaller%20than%20a%20neighbourhood.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20more%20space%20for%20public%20use%2C%20help%20biodiversity%2C%20promote%20sustainable%20transportation%2C%20and%20even%20encourage%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20superblocks%20was%20introduced%20in%20Barcelona%20as%20part%20of%20its%202013-2018%20Urban%20Mobility%20Plan%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20redo%20120%20intersections.%20Currently%2C%20the%20city%20is%20working%20on%20redesigning%20one-third%20of%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20L%E2%80%99Eixample%20district%2C%20originally%20planned%20by%20Ildefons%20Cerd%C3%A0.%20Starting%20in%202022%2C%20the%20city%20is%20focusing%20on%20remodelling%2021%20streets%20by%202030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20reliable%20EV%20infrastructure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20component%20of%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20its%20focus%20on%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F195571%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-deshla-electric-three-wheeler-recharge-home-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs).%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20city%20has%20worked%20hard%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20by%20investing%20in%20EV%20infrastructure%2C%20even%20offering%20incentives%20for%20EV%20owners.%20The%20city%20has%20installed%20over%201%2C000%20charging%20stations%2C%20for%20electric%20cars%20and%20given%20tax%20breaks%20and%20free%20parking%20for%20EV%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20also%20introduced%20electric%20buses%20and%20taxis%20into%20its%20public%20transportation%20network%2C%20further%20reducing%20emissions%20from%20traditional%20fuel-powered%20vehicles.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%2C%20particularly%20SDG%207%3A%20Affordable%20and%20Clean%20Energy%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20%E2%80%9Censure%20access%20to%20affordable%2C%20reliable%2C%20sustainable%20and%20modern%20energy%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20promote%20cleaner%20transportation%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20expanding%20its%20network%20of%20cycling%20and%20pedestrian%20lanes%2C%20with%20over%201%2C000%20kilometres%20of%20these%20pathways%20now%20under%20construction.%20Public%20bike-sharing%20systems%20have%20also%20been%20rolled%20out%20across%20the%20city%2C%20with%20400%20stations%20available%20to%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20fume-free%20mobility%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunities%20need%20to%20start%20demanding%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20broader%20roads%20and%20better%20flyovers%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20demand%20clean%20air%20from%20our%20political%20class.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spanish%20city%20has%20also%20placed%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20public%20transportation.%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20extensive%20public%20transit%20system%2C%20including%20buses%2C%20trams%2C%20and%20metro%20lines%2C%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20travel%20without%20relying%20on%20private%20cars.%20The%20city%20operates%20a%20number%20of%20initiatives%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20use%20public%20transport%20and%20adopt%20cleaner%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202135px)%20100vw%2C%202135px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tram%20in%20Barcelona%20traveling%20along%20a%20city%20street%2C%20part%20of%20the%20city's%20sustainable%20public%20transit%20network.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118.jpeg%202135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-768x960.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-1229x1536.jpeg%201229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-1638x2048.jpeg%201638w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-1200x1500.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384044%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBarcelona%E2%80%99s%20public%20transit%2C%20including%20trams%2C%20promotes%20cleaner%20and%20car-free%20travel%20options%20(Representational%20image)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20during%20times%20of%20high%20pollution%2C%20the%20city%20increases%20public%20transport%20services%20by%2010%25%20and%20offers%20discounted%20%E2%80%98T-aire%E2%80%99%20multi-ride%20tickets%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20use%20them.%20They%20also%20have%20schemes%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98T%20Verda%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20a%20three-year%20free%20transit%20pass%20to%20people%20who%20scrap%20old%2C%20polluting%20vehicles%20and%20commit%20to%20not%20purchasing%20another%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20addressing%20emissions%20from%20private%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20air%20quality%20improves%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Barcelona%20is%20observing%20socio-economic%20benefits.%20There%20has%20been%20a%2030%25%20rise%20in%20commercial%20activity%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20with%20reduced%20vehicle%20traffic%20and%20more%20pedestrian-friendly%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExpanding%20green%20spaces%20for%20cleaner%20air%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarcelona%20has%20also%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328522%2Fhow-nature-based-solutions-can-help-build-climate-change-resilience-wri-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eurban%20greening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20goal%20of%20increasing%20its%20green%20spaces.%20They%20plan%20on%20adding%20more%20than%20160%20hectares%20of%20green%20space%20by%202030%2C%20which%20will%20help%20improve%20air%20quality%2C%20absorb%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20manage%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect.%20Green%20spaces%20like%20parks%2C%20gardens%2C%20and%20tree-lined%20streets%20provide%20a%20natural%20buffer%20to%20pollution.%20The%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20for%20Living%E2%80%9D%20initiative%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Barcelona%20Tree%20Master%20Plan%2C%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20tree%20cover%20and%20better%20its%20natural%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jha%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndeed%2C%20it%20%5Bair%20pollution%5D%20is%20no%20more%20just%20an%20environmental%20crisis%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20public%20health%20crisis.%20There%20is%20enough%20empirical%20data%20and%20research%20that%20talks%20about%20the%20grave%20public%20health%20impact%20it%20has.%20We%20cannot%20fix%20the%20problem%20through%20individual%20efforts%20like%20air%20purifiers%20or%20the%20luxury%20of%20leaving%20the%20city.%20We%20need%20a%20collective%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Endolla%20Barcelona%2C%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20electromobility%20network%2C%20the%20use%20of%20EVs%20prevented%20the%20emission%20of%208%2C989%20tons%20of%20CO2%20in%202023.%20Barcelona%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20sustainable%20urban%20development%20with%20improved%20air%20quality.%20The%20city%20sets%20a%20global%20benchmark%20for%20cleaner%20cities%20and%20shows%20how%20sustainable%20urban%20planning%20can%20simultaneously%20improve%20public%20health%2C%20economic%20vitality%2C%20and%20environmental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd5%2FN1529189.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETransforming%20our%20world%3A%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Published%20on%2021%20October%202015.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732854590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-mobile-1732080263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D384037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Learn%20how%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20urban%20planning%2C%20green%20initiatives%2C%20and%20public%20transport%20reforms%20offer%20actionable%20solutions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20air%20pollution%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384037%2Fbarcelona-air-quality-india-pollution-solution-delhi%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22She%20Gave%20up%20Her%20Own%20D